Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说我是无信仰者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I'm a nonbeliever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you're not, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅森先生  什么是新联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Mason, what is the New Coalition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是  领队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are, team leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾士芬尼指引下光明的下一代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The next generation to walk the Espheni path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将拯救地球及人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will save the Earth and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我们要拯救自己的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First, we save our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And how will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到他们  拉响警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll find them and raise the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And why will we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我爱他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好  梅森先生  请座吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice work, Mr. Mason. You may take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你上前来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd now like to invite you up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好  梅森先生  我都差点让你骗了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice work, Mr. Mason. You almost fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是个特殊的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Today is a very special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉要毕业了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila is graduating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}午餐后  老时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉的父母就是所谓的"叛乱分子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila's parents are what some call "insurgents"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说"恐怖分子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or "terrorists."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的一些成人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some adults on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对政府和领导人过于愤世嫉俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have become so cynical about governments and leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法信任我们的艾士芬尼兄弟们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they have a hard time trusting our Espheni brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉的父母就是反叛者的成员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila's parents are part of this web of rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会引发无谓的攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is launching unprovoked attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好  我们截获了希拉母亲发的一条消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Luckily, we intercepted a message from Sheila's mother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问道  是否有人见过她的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Asking if anyone had seen her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She really loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1} I love her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你准备怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what are you going to do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到她  拉响警报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll find her and raise the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要在...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她带我回到藏身之处之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She takes me back to their hiding place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就可以拯救所有叛乱者了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we can save all the insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全正确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意领我们背诵宣言吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you lead us in the pledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是天赐之福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Earth is a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新联盟必须和艾士芬尼兄弟们一同保护地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The New Coalition must protect it with our Espheni brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们同心协力  必将共创美好新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Joined together, we will build a beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是疯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么跟着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你的存货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm here for your stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见你溜到迅猎兽背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw you slide behind the Skitters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃它们吃剩的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lapping up their crumbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或从无力反抗的人那里偷食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}stealing food from decent people who can't defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尽力获取所需  和别人没有分别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took what I could, no different than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况你和梅森掌管这里这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Besides, you and Mason have been in charge all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我们成了什么样子  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look where we are.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是"我们"  珀普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's this "we," Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知  你可是个非常称职的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as I can tell, you're doing a perfectly fine job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无道德懦夫叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of behaving like a craven, immoral turncoat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里只有自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把藏货交出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hand over your stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己来拿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀普  韦弗  我们知道你在下面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pope, weaver! yeah. We know you're down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人跟踪你  你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody followed you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来  你们俩是一伙的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, you two are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不是  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No!  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你一直在偷东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I know you've been stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知道你藏在哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just didn't know where you kept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谢谢你全家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for that, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  小伙子们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen, boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们来这的目的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm here for the same reason you are --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到这里藏着的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to find whatever food is hidden down here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后分发给大家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and distribute it to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分个屁  我们饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Screw that. We're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要吃东西...  马上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna eat... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少给我动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别浪费时间了  珀普  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't waste your time, Pope. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-丁甘  -汤姆·梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dingaan.  - Tom Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你很高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是短波电台吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that a shortwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  而且还能用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, man. And it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果外面还有人在听的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is, if there's someone out there to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以试试看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're welcome to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭敬不如从命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尔说你是南非来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hal tells me you're from South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh...yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰内斯堡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Johannesburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了妻儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I lost my wife and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次入侵还是壁垒落下的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the initial invasion or when the walls came down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次入侵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后一直潜逃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Been running ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从三所艾士芬尼监狱逃脱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}escaping Espheni prisons -- three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里士满  格林斯博罗  夏洛特市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Richmond, Greensboro, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑蜂兽在我往南卡罗来纳州穿越的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hornets found me crossing into South Carolina,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我抓到这里来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说说越狱的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me about the escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每座监狱各不相同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every camp is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个共同之处  绿色壁垒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but one thing is a constant -- the Green Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要越过它  你需要这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To go over it, you need one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉第屏蔽服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A faraday suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在翻越电网的时候  让电流从周遭流过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It allows electricity to flow around me as I climb the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:16:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是物理学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a physicist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电气工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Electrical lineman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以教你怎么制造  只要给我找到铜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will teach you how to build one if you help me find copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有铜  屏蔽服无法使用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without it, the suit won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有人藏了废金属\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know some guys that are hoarding some scrap metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以找他们谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏蔽服是很不错  但只能一个人穿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The suit's great, but it's only for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让所有人都出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to get everybody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们要想办法把电网电源关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, we need to figure out a way to cut the power to the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑蜂兽带我飞入这个营地时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the Hornets flew me into this camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了一个传感器连接一条链条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw a sensor and a tether coming off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看不到通向哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I couldn't see where it led.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你觉得那是电源线吗  -有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you think that tether's a power cord?  - Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样  我还真能用上你的屏蔽服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if that's true, then maybe I could use one of your suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以翻过电网  剪断链条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could climb the wall, cut the tether,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断电网的电源线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it will bring the power to the walls down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你不是一个人  知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dad, it's not all on you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还需要想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We still need to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让几百人都出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how to get hundreds of people out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以分散迅猎兽的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could cause a distraction, have all the Skitter guards
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家越狱的时候  让它们跟着我走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}follow me while everybody else escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们还需要一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then we'd still need someone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上屏蔽服翻过电网\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to get in the suit and climb the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们又回到先前的问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That brings us back to the missing piece of the puzzle --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂周围的迅猎兽到底在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the Skitters are clustered near that church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来答案都在那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like all the answers are right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也能对付他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could have taken those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么比看你被揍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, there's nothing I would have liked better
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能让我高兴的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than to see you get your ass kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他们有刀  而且还以为我们是同伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had knives, and they thought that we were partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想因为你死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not getting killed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-希望他们喜欢豆子  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, I hope they like beans. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存货就是八罐豆子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My stash consisted of eight cans of beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不早说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我要东山再起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, man, one day, I'm gonna be back in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  我得保证我的名号不倒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Till then, I got a reputation to uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时都打算揍你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was ready to kick your ass back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也很愿意现在动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I'm happy to do it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你今天说的最智慧的一句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, now, that's the smartest thing you have said all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  你还得先睡会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What? You need to take a nap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是需要个热身运动  能量饮料什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You need to stretch out, a little shot of gatorade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么啦  -你能闭嘴吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - Would you shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奇斯  我是汤姆·梅森  能听到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cochise, this is Tom Mason. Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奇斯  我是汤姆·梅森  能收到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cochise? This is tom mason. Are you out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆·梅森  收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom Mason, I read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我父亲发现他给我的通讯器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father would be surprised to find the communicator he left me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被改装成了更低端的设备肯定要惊讶了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has been retrofitted to a lesser technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得与时俱进嘛  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got to -- you got to change with the times, my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是倒退也没办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even if it's backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这件事很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know it's a bit of a crapshoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们需要食物和补给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we're hurting for food and supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的队伍和你们的集中营之间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are substantial Espheni forces
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大量的艾士芬尼势力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between my team and your camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么新消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What else is new?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A great deal, as a matter of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确认了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have confirmed that the Espheni
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾士芬尼在建造新的能源站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are constructing a new power station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用来给以前的电力网供能的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this, uh, designed to power a grid like the one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力网和在我来之前你摧毁的那种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. That grid, along with the Espheni jamming device
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾士芬尼屏蔽仪都是防御措施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you destroyed before my arrival, were defensive measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的能源是艾士芬尼用以攻击的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The new power source would allow the Espheni to go on offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用以攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On offense?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不像什么好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That... doesn't sound very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题到时候再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, w-w-well, let's burn that bridge when we come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在最大的问题是没有食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right now I've got some very hungry people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我没法给你弄到食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot get food to you at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果你能逃出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, if you do manage to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是知道你能在哪找到食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can tell you where there is food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就将来再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we got that to look forward to, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有个好消息告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do have one piece of encouraging news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的一架无人机发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of our recon drones observed children
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有孩子被送去了南边一个集中营\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}being transported to a camp south of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为马特也在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We believe Matt has been taken there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把他救出来吗  科奇斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you get him? Cochise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先和我队伍的人商量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must confer with my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和谁商量都行  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no, w-w-- yes, confer with whoever you want, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是我现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but that's about the -- the worst thing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最无法拖延的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you could dangle in front of me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他父亲  却没法保护他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm his father, and I can't protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能救救他吗  求你了  科奇斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you get to him, please? Please, Cochise.
