Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去重新接受教育以便迎接新秩序的来临\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Re-education to help them be successful in the new order.
