Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾士芬尼和人类联手  由混血带领\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Espheni and human together, led by the Hybrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Hybrid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混血才是我们的未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Hybrid is our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚蕾克西  是她吗  是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lexi. Is this her? Is this --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是她吗  我女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is this who you're talking about? My daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是你说的未来吗  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is she the future? Is she the future you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我  你们把她带到哪儿去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me! Where is she being taken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要  -她在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Oh, no. - Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要  -你们把她带到哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Oh, no. - Where is she being taken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别插队  梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey. Can't cut in line, Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人会把你脑袋弄下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These people will cut your head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.26,0:22:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见我妹妹还要排队吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not waiting in line to see my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attaboy. 
