Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要赐予我们的  她有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}... us all of her offerings. She's got --
