Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要想拦住你是轻而易举的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we want to stop you, we can.
