Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我是她哥哥所以她也许会听我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I'm her older brother and she might listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和无信仰者站在一起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause you've aligned yourself with a nonbeliever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说卡达尔博士吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean Dr. Kadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他有名字的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样做  你是个医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are you acting like this? You're a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当医生也没法保证我安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Being a doctor didn't keep me safe, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚蕾克西可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lexi did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她取走了我的眼线虫  使我不被控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She removed the scales from my eyes, and I was healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她救了我  所以我要保护她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She saved me. And I will protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚蕾克西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lexi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以  进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独谈  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only you, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里难道不美吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't it beautiful in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.24,0:23:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外面好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So much nicer than it is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有喧嚣  也无吵闹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the noise, the crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,械甲怪的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Mechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.46,0:23:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家对此津津乐道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a story these people will never stop telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为是你毁了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They think you destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到空气中的电力开始聚集\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could feel the electricity gathering in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了械甲怪启动时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could feel the frequency necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所需要的电力频率\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the Mech to operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后械甲怪就停下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the Mech came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达尔博士认为你有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Kadar thinks you're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想帮你检查一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wants to examine you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢尔德不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lourdes says no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢尔德想要通过控制你来得到权力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lourdes is trying to gain power by controlling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不听命于她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I answer to a higher power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚蕾克西  我觉得你有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lexi... I think you're in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不相信这里的人能保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm not convinced that the people here have your back.
