Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话能别跟庙里的签一个调调吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you please stop talking like a damn fortune cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我怎么说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How would you like me to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教育我如何与他人交流吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you have a manual for how I should communicate?
