Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是莎士比亚  或是你的上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or Shakespeare or your own God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.35,0:24:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.36,0:24:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚蕾克西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lexi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争就要开始了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is a war on, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们的家人  依旧不知所踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}our family -- we have no idea where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  马特  哈尔  你妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dad, Matt, Hal, your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都会来的  本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're all coming, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.99,0:24:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很快就会来  在那之前  我们很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll all be here soon. Until then, we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.92,0:24:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不记得壁垒落下时的样子了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't remember what it was like when the Barriers fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.93,0:24:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.52,0:24:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你抱着我  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember you holding me to your chest, 
