Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.52,0:24:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的  我是你哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will. I'm -- I'm your brother.
