Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.28,0:25:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你希望我去找卡达尔博士  我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you want me to see Dr. Kadar, I will.
