Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.59,0:25:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得我们应该等等韦弗上校吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you think we ought to wait for Colonel Weaver?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总得想办法收集信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to get the information one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.16,0:25:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道它们不会直接杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do you know they're not just gonna take you up there and kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.25,0:25:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他它们想杀我  我早死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If they wanted me dead, I'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.58,0:25:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-爸爸  -它们有很多杀我的机会  哈尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dad -- - They've had plenty of chances, Hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.65,0:25:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.85,0:25:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出什么事  你要取代我的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And if anything goes wrong, I need you to take over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.88,0:25:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These people trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.58,0:25:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.59,0:25:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.85,0:26:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.67,0:26:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.26,0:26:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆·梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom Mason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.45,0:26:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想找我吗  我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want me?! Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.99,0:26:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.60,0:26:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.10,0:27:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎啊  汤姆·梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome, Tom Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.18,0:27:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.84,0:27:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.80,0:27:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他的名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know his name --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.50,0:27:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位被你用来传话的倒霉孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this poor kid you're using as a mouthpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.73,0:27:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.85,0:27:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.78,0:27:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢现身出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you gonna show yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.91,0:27:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你太害怕  不敢自己动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or are you too afraid to come out and do your own dirty work?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.97,0:27:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么要动手的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing dirty to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.45,0:27:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有个提议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a simple proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.81,0:27:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.98,0:27:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打仗时需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need you to be part of our war effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.46,0:27:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.97,0:27:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你帮我们打败一个强大的共同敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You will help us thwart a greater common enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.83,0:28:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你就救下了你的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and, in so doing, spare your own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.58,0:28:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别提我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't mention my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.13,0:28:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解你  汤姆·梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know more about you than just your name, Tom Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.76,0:28:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有共同敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't have a common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.63,0:28:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔姆是我们的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Volm are our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.86,0:28:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起即将到来的危险  沃尔姆根本不值一提\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Volm are no match for the danger that's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.46,0:28:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What danger would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.82,0:28:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法想象的强大力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A force far greater than your mind can comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.38,0:28:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But defeating them
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.29,0:28:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了自己的星球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is why we strayed so far from our own galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.57,0:28:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路上收集了这么多资源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why we collected resources
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.92,0:28:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了打败他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from every planet and moon along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.13,0:28:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大战很快就要开始了  为了面对战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The great battle is coming, and in order to face it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.08,0:28:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须组建一支崭新的前线部队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we are creating a new, elite, frontline army.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.79,0:28:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你说的就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, is that where the, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.12,0:28:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些又黑又大的飞虫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}big, black, flying things come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.71,0:28:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是我们守卫之中的叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those are traitors from the ranks of our guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.33,0:28:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅猎兽叛党吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rebel Skitters?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.24,0:28:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过基因改造  变成无意识的无人机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Genetically altered into mindless drones...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.93,0:28:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全听命于我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}completely under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.48,0:28:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由意志可能会变得很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Free will can be dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.93,0:28:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点不用我说你也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I don't have to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.19,0:28:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的守卫虽表现出色  但能力有限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other guards performed admirably, but they are limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.23,0:28:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人类的孩子脊甲化才是长期之策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Harnessing human children proved to be unpredictable long-term.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.46,0:29:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正为战争培养更聪颖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are perfecting a smarter, more plentiful soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.56,0:29:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及更大量的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.03,0:29:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑选出一部分素质优良的成人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Selected human adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.35,0:29:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的身躯已完成生长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your bodies have finished growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.16,0:29:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格与素质已充分定型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your personalities and predispositions are set.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.99,0:29:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是早就在凯伦身上试验过这套吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Didn't you already try that with Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.18,0:29:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果可不甚如意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That didn't work out too well for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.37,0:29:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们疏忽了  没有除去凯伦的自由意志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We neglected to strip Karen of free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.93,0:29:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已改正了错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We corrected that mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.74,0:29:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在48小时候后准时开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will begin transforming our selected human adults
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.70,0:29:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转化被选中的成人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in precisely 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.62,0:29:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们拒绝服从呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happens when we refuse to go along?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.20,0:29:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止我们所做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you willingly go along
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.59,0:29:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们何曾顺意服从过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with anything we've chosen to do so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.34,0:29:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会挑选你们种族中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will select the best
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.68,0:29:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最聪颖最优秀的人加入我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the brightest of your race to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.50,0:29:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们花费数月时间才完善好转化过程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a process we've taken months to perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.74,0:29:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们谈话之际  准备已然在进行当中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're doing it even now, as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.62,0:29:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何作出抵抗的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anyone who resists will simply serve
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.46,0:29:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会成为失去意识的空壳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in a less-conscious form.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.46,0:29:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.39,0:29:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll find out soon enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.53,0:29:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你拒绝我们的提议的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because your family will be first in line
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.56,0:29:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人将会是首批的实验对象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if you refuse our offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.70,0:30:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pope!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.66,0:30:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.10,0:30:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这是电网的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wait a second. That's part of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.74,0:30:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着在电网的另一头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Which means that whatever is on the other side of it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.80,0:30:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是墙外的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is outside the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.21,0:30:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有日光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.95,0:30:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正是我们所需要的领袖人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the kind of leader we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.34,0:30:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你肯协助转化计划的完成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help this transition go smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.20,0:30:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人将被赦免\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and your family will be spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.30,0:30:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要马上听到你的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need your answer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.50,0:30:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做出决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have a decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.31,0:30:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的家人能免于加入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and your family can be spared
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.91,0:30:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将发生的伟大的转换计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the great transformation that is to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.63,0:30:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的领袖能力以及勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your leadership and courage
